HEADWORD: Saginate
<hw>Sag"i*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>saginatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>saginare</ets> to fat, fr.
<ets>sagina</ets> stuffing.]</ety> <def>To make fat; to pamper.</def>
